flowchart LR
  subgraph Client
    A[Browser / PWA]
    SW[Service Worker]
  end

  A <--> SW
  A -->|HTTPS| V[Vercel Edge + Serverless]
  V --> N[Next.js App Router]
  N --> SA[Server Actions]
  SA --> S[Supabase]

  subgraph S[Supabase]
    PG[(PostgreSQL + RLS)]
    AUTH[Auth]
    ST[Storage]
  end

  N -->|SSR / Streaming| A
